name: JS Errors Generator Home Page

### Welcome to JS Errors Generator Home Page
JS Errors Generator is a project that aims to 

1. ease the way errors defined in Javascript
2. bear i18n in mind
3. both for browsers and servers
4. ease of exchanging
5. both web and none web
6. for restful apis
7. unique id for the same error, which can be exchanged through projects
